headline: Some Boring Stocks Are Beating Big Techs. Plus, You Can Sleep at Night.
summary: Apollo Global chief economist Torsten Sløk offers investors some winning long-term stocks plays from Tractor Supply, Domino’s Pizza, and Old Dominion Freight that beat some of the Mag Seven.
